size: x-large;\">4. 大埔有4歲男童在家玩耍時意外反鎖於主人房，其後男童到露台查看時不慎從12樓失足墮樓，現時情况危殆。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2iZ0GpZ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2iZ0GpZ&d=LocyWrPuCwFUSFEj7z139ZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=7f5848c2\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2iZ0GpZ</a> (明報)<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2k8DZBF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2k8DZBF&d=LocyWrPuCwFUSFEj7z139ZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=f398869b\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2k8DZBF</a> (東方日報)<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2je4scQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2je4scQ&d=LocyWrPuCwFUSFEj7z139ZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=8b7cb8ba\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2je4scQ</a> (星島日報)<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2iQ2tdO\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2iQ2tdO&d=LocyWrPuCwFUSFEj7z139ZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=c0ce64d3\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2iQ2tdO</a> (蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">5. 城市規劃委員會將開會審議啟德分區計劃大綱圖，建議將四幅原本興建私人住宅的土地改劃作公營房屋發展，提供約6000個單位。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2jSc8SL\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2jSc8SL&d=LocyWrPuCwFUSFEj7z139ZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=e9de057e\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2jSc8SL</a> (明報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">6. 運輸及房屋局向立法會提交新一年施政綱領文件，指港鐵沙中線「大圍至紅磡段」料可提早半年於2019年年中通車。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2jEEkuL\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2jEEkuL&d=LocyWrPuCwFUSFEj7z139ZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=7a162615\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2jEEkuL</a> (東方日報)<br />\n<br />\n兩岸:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 國家主席習近平在聯合國日內瓦總部發表演說，主張共同推進構建人類命運共同體偉大進程、開放型世界經濟體制及多邊主義的世界秩序等。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2iYMqOf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2iYMqOf&d=LocyWrPuCwFUSFEj7z139ZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=085cb537\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2iYMqOf</a> (明報)<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2iHoRec\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2iHoRec&d=LocyWrPuCwFUSFEj7z139ZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=75325cdb\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2iHoRec</a> (星島日報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2. 重慶市第四屆人大第五次會議閉幕，市委副書記張國清當選為重慶市長。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2k8xtuS\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2k8xtuS&d=LocyWrPuCwFUSFEj7z139ZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=0b7b8d6a\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2k8xtuS</a> (明報)<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2jScVDd\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2jScVDd&d=LocyWrPuCwFUSFEj7z139ZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=ec0181bd\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2jScVDd</a> (東方日報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3. 廣東省第十二屆人大第五次會議開幕，代省長馬興瑞作政府工作報告，提到廣東去年的GDP增長達7.4%，預計今年增長為7%以上。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2je3z4f\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2je3z4f&d=LocyWrPuCwFUSFEj7z139ZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=b427a3d7\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2je3z4f</a> (明報)<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2iHwIIH\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2iHwIIH&d=LocyWrPuCwFUSFEj7z139ZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=0a998814\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2iHwIIH</a> (東方日報)<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2k68uEl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2k68uEl&d=LocyWrPuCwFUSFEj7z139ZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=4e623124\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2k68uEl</a> (星島日報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">4. 台灣的前行政院長游錫堃到美國準備出席美國總統就職儀式，北京當局表示反對。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2iHweST\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2iHweST&d=LocyWrPuCwFUSFEj7z139ZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=361090ed\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2iHweST</a> (東方日報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">5. 山西運城新絳縣三林鎮汾河橋有一輛裝載近三十噸有毒粗苯的罐車與一輛客車碰撞，導致罐車跌入黃河支流汾河並破裂出現粗苯洩漏，罐車上兩人死亡。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2k6bqAE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2k6bqAE&d=LocyWrPuCwFUSFEj7z139ZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=c110d76a\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2k6bqAE</a> (東方日報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">6. 就廣東佛山連續發生的兩宗巴士爆炸案，佛山警方公佈指有一名疑犯已被拘捕。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2iYU62N\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2iYU62N&d=LocyWrPuCwFUSFEj7z139ZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=14be3350\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2iYU62N</a> (東方日報)<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2jRXVFn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2jRXVFn&d=LocyWrPuCwFUSFEj7z139ZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=19b3b964\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2jRXVFn</a> (星島日報)"},{"pid":"cd57984b876308b142312745aa28984ca831188d","tid":87501,"uid":68591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T01:03:21.000Z","msg":"國際:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 特朗普過渡團隊宣佈提名喬治亞州前州長珀杜出任農業部長。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2iPYrCg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2iPYrCg&d=LocyWrPuCwFUSFEj7z139ZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=ed0828f2\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2iPYrCg</a> (東方日報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2. 美國多名國民警衞軍士兵及警察被調派往首都華盛頓負責總統就職典禮的保安工作，以防恐怖襲擊和民眾示威衝擊會場。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2k8HiJ7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2k8HiJ7&d=LocyWrPuCwFUSFEj7z139ZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=c45a6011\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2k8HiJ7</a> (東方日報)<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2iYN3XS\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2iYN3XS&d=LocyWrPuCwFUSFEj7z139ZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=03965ff9\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2iYN3XS</a> (星島日報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3. 伊朗首都德黑蘭一幢大樓發生大火，200名消防員奉召到場滅火，後來整幢大樓突然倒塌，造成多名消防員死傷。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2jEMAet\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2jEMAet&d=LocyWrPuCwFUSFEj7z139ZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=fc4f1636\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2jEMAet</a> (明報)<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2jEKUSc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2jEKUSc&d=LocyWrPuCwFUSFEj7z139ZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=869d48a9\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2jEKUSc</a> (東方日報)<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2jE7oD2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2jE7oD2&d=LocyWrPuCwFUSFEj7z139ZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=5fbe573b\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2jE7oD2</a> (星島日報)<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2jE2UfA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2jE2UfA&d=LocyWrPuCwFUSFEj7z139ZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=646c0268\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2jE2UfA</a> (蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">4. 意大利中部因地震誘發雪崩，有山區一家酒店遭積雪掩埋，酒店內的住客和職員失蹤。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2k8KOmP\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2k8KOmP&d=LocyWrPuCwFUSFEj7z139ZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=0dd665c1\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2k8KOmP</a> (明報)<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2iPYw8X\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2iPYw8X&d=LocyWrPuCwFUSFEj7z139ZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=17583e43\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2iPYw8X</a> (東方日報)<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2jESuMw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2jESuMw&d=LocyWrPuCwFUSFEj7z139ZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=cd002225\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2jESuMw</a> (星島日報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">5. 岡比亞總統賈梅任期屆滿但拒絕下台，新總統巴羅（Adama Barrow）計劃在鄰國塞內加爾的岡比亞大使館宣誓就職，西非15個國家的軍隊已集結岡比亞邊境威迫賈梅交權。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2jtIvrb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.l